<text><body>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D12.8820.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead>新菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>經一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><cb:div><p xml:id="pD12p0001a0201"><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0001001" n="0001001"/>新菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>經<g ref="#CB14426">󳡚</g>諸眾生大小每日念阿<g ref="#CB12752">󳇐</g>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/>佛一百口今載大熟湏人万〃億湏牛万
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/>〃頭勸諸眾生斷<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>脩善禾丘無人
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D12.8820.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0101" n="0002a0101"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0101" n="0002a0101"/><g ref="#CB15756">𠬧</g><anchor xml:id="end0002a0101"/>苅苐一病死苐二卆死苐三赤眼死
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>苐四腫病死苐五產生死苐六患腹。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/><p xml:id="pD12p0002a0301">有眼眾生冩一本免一身冩兩本免一
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/>門冩三本免一村若不信者即滅門。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/><p xml:id="pD12p0002a0501">此經<g ref="#CB30130">󷖲</g>西亰州正月二日盛中時雷<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0501" n="0002a0501"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0501" n="0002a0501"/>鳴<anchor xml:id="end0002a0501"/>雨
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/>聲有一石下大如<g ref="#CB08128">㚈</g>遂兩片即見此經
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>報諸眾生今載饒患。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="1"><cb:jhead>新菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>經一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body>
